Don't Press the button.
Your party enters a room. The doors slam behind you, and you see a bright red button with a sigh saying 'DO NOT PUSH'. What do you do?
Push the button.::Really!? They told you not to push the button. Doors open in front of you and you can proceed to the next room.::Boss
Don't push the button.::Somehow, you manage to resist the temptation to not push the button. Minutes pass. Then days. Then years. You are starving, almost dead, and then a door infront of you opens.::Boss